Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\an8}Aku mual...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\an8}Jangan muntah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau lemah sekali, Kak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jangan tertawa, Nazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, bagaimana setelah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau baik-baik saja? Mau air?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mau...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Kalau begitu, ayo kita beli air, Nazuna. - Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Toserba mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dengar, kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku sedang tak sehat sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Akibatnya, aku merasa sangat tak aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalian mau meninggalkanku sendirian seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jangan bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Salah satu dari kalian harus menemaniku di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nazuna saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak mau Nanakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei! Ko ini bukan untuk disewa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Pemeluk profesional. - Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau pemeluk profesional, 'kan? Apa ini cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Akan kuborong semua airnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa menjadi begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ayo ceritakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Agar pikiranku teralihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Cerita...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pada suatu hari, ada...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau mau mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ada siswa SMP yang biasa-biasa saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}yaitu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Siswa yang biasa-biasa saja? Aku langsung bisa membayangkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lalu, banyak hal terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku kewalahan menjalaninya,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.05,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi beginilah sekarang keadaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku dulu bertemu vampir
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dan melihat orang berciuman di jembatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Setelah tersadar orang dewasa pun bisa mengalami hal memalukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}aku bertemu wanita yang menangis karena lelah bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Serta pria yang cintanya ditolak, lalu menjadi gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Atau para pelayan yang berkata, "Moe moe gyun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Juga, orang-orang yang entah suka menggoda atau memang ramah saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku pun tahu bahwa vampir juga punya kepribadian yang berbeda-beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.80,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Setelah bertemu banyak orang yang tak mungkin kujumpai di hidup lamaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}aku tahu orang dewasa itu ada banyak ragamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku selalu mengira orang dewasa makhluk yang sangat berbeda dari anak-anak,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi ternyata mereka hanya kelanjutan dari kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Benar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nona Detektif, apa ada momen ketika kau sadar sudah dewasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Menua bukan berarti menjadi dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku yakin banyak orang yang mengalami jatuh bangun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}selama proses mendewasakan diri mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi mungkin aku tak tahu seperti apa jatuh bangun itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Orang-orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tempat kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Teman-teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Percintaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau merasakan "jatuh"-nya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak boleh langsung seperti ini, harus bertahap...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau berhak bicara begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pemeluknya tak mau memelukku. Jadi, kupaksa saja dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baiklah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak pernah tidur dengan orang karena tinggal bersama orang tuaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Keluargaku hancur karena vampir,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi ayahku juga bermasalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Logikaku memang menerima semua itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi aku akan kehilangan alasan hidup jika tak menciptakan musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sekarang, pikiran itu sudah lenyap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Makanya aku mau hidup normal seperti manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hidup normal itu sangat berat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lamunanmu selalu menghadirkan ketidakpuasan pada hidupmu yang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}"Kenapa aku melakukannya?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}"Untuk apa sepuluh tahun terakhir ini?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa semua itu sia-sia saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku pulang! Bagaimana kondisimu, Kak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Sut! - Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia baru saja tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa yang mau kau bahas di luar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa artinya hidup normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nona Detektif bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei, kau minum lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kurasa Nona Detektif mau menjadi normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak mungkin. Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau tak sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi itu memang mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia memang sudah aneh dari awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Meski dia tak mengenal vampir pun, kurasa dia tak akan menjadi normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Kau juga sama, Ko. - Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Asai dan Mahiru Seki juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalian semua orang-orang aneh yang percaya diri kalian normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? "Kalian semua"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kedua orang itu memang agak aneh, tapi aku lumayan normal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mereka semua pasti mencap yang lain aneh dan mengaku dirinya normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}"Tidak penting jika aku aneh."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau pola pikir kalian begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ujung dari rangkaian semua kejadian ini
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}adalah upaya bunuh diri yang dipersiapkan matang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi gagal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nona Detektif bersikap seakan sudah melupakannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}tapi sulit mengisi lubang besar di hatinya yang sudah terbentuk satu dekade lamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Entah apa yang bisa kita lakukan untuknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin dia tidur sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, ayo kita berjalan-jalan saja agar tak membangunkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}VAMP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Selamat datang... Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nazuna dan Yamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Hei. - Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pas sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami bingung karena kekurangan staf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalian memang penolong kami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Cepat ke belakang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hari ini, kami tidak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yamori, kau duduk saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sudah kubilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku datang bukan untuk bekerja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Berarti aku boleh minum bir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Syukurlah dia mau bekerja, meski sambil mengeluh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi aku mau dia menyapa tamu terlebih dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Suasana hatinya pasti akan selalu gembira, asalkan dia bisa minum bir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak disangka, ternyata dia cocok bekerja menjadi pelayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Apa? - Halo, Tuan Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}LG?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Segelas penuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Terima kasih atas tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, apa yang membawamu ke sini hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Astaga, maafkan aku! Kafe ini tempat Nona Midori bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, kau tentunya datang untuk menemui Nona Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei, istilah itu berasal dari anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Wah! Kata "kurorekishi" itu dari anime, ya? Aku baru tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Moe moe gyun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Imutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Cita rasanya makin enak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hal apa yang menentukan kau cocok atau tak saat bekerja di suatu bidang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Pertanyaan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi pertanyaan bagus tak selalu punya jawaban bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kurasa ada banyak faktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Seperti tak menganggap serius omongan tamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}atau pandai menghadapi tamu, atau memang suka minum alkohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi di luar semua itu, kurasa karena kau suka orang-orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Benar sekali, kau tak akan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jelek sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kabura rupanya merasa begitu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak mau membunuhmu, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tetaplah terjaga sampai kau merasa puas dengan harimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Satu soda melon. - Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Bersulang! - Tunggu sebentar, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Di mana aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kacamataku...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aduh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami datang untuk melepas penat setelah bekerja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Wah, kalian datang bertiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tumben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa itu? Untuk kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, dia bilang untuk diminum bersama semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Semacam persembahan darinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Sudahlah, akan kuminum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tolong buka sumbat botolnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau akan gugup jika sumbatnya meletus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu norak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Insiden detektif itu memang menyulitkan. Kau sampai jatuh bangun, ya, Yamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak, maaf, kau menjadi ikut terlibat juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak apa-apa, kami tahu ceritanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi aku masih jengkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi kita bisa membereskan semua ini tanpa harus kehilangan satu orang pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, mari kita rayakan keberhasilan itu. Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Wah, ini enak sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Love memang yang terbaik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Di mana Kabura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia bilang akan menyusul ke sini selepas kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak usah datang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jangan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Midori, sepertinya sudah saatnya membawa keturunanmu ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya. Seri saja membawa keturunannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Terima kasih. - Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sudah kubilang, ketiga keturunanku sibuk bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, tiga orang yang bertampang tajir itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin kau bisa menyebut mereka dengan bertampang elegan saja, Seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau dengar itu, Midori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi Love sendiri bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}"Hamba menolaknya karena tak pantas menerima kehormatan itu."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, jangan memaksanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\an8}"Hamba?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lagi pula, semuanya pasti akan suka dia jika bertemu dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami makin penasaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Yamori saja sudah berkumpul bersama kita dari dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bahkan ketika dia belum menjadi keturunan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Memangnya kau yang mengajaknya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Memang aku yang mengajaknya duluan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Itu aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku yang pertama memperhatikan Yamori
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}karena tahu Nazuna sedang dekat dengan seorang manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Menakutkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau lugu. Jadi, aku mengawasimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku juga tahu kau diam-diam mengisap darah pemabuk seperti maling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa maksudmu kau tahu? Menakutkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Menyedihkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Setidaknya, jagalah harga dirimu sebagai vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Diam! Memangnya kau ibuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei, kenapa kau malah diam? Mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nazuna pasti terbiasa diasuh Kabura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak, untuk apa terbiasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin karena kau suka keluyuran, dia menjadi khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Benar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, aku dikenal suka keluyuran, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lalu, bagaimana kelanjutan hubunganmu dengan Yamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kelanjutan... Itu hal pribadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Kalau begitu, ceritaku dan Akkun saja. - Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak usah, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa tak mau? Coba dengarkan, kau pasti akan menangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Cintaku dengan Love itu baru namanya cinta sejati!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Cinta sejati? Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Tapi cinta kita sejati, 'kan, Seri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin ini pendapatku saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Sudahlah, Akkun! - Aku pribadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ayo, cepat kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku merasa sangat sepi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kepalaku sakit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}dan perutku mual sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Saatnya wanita bergosip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bulannya terang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nona Detektif mencoba membuat malam terasa sepi dan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin ini contoh malam yang tak diinginkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa aku benar-benar senang jika malam tak selalu tenang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau sedang apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nazuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ekspresimu selalu begitu setiap kali memikirkan hal rumit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ekspresiku seperti itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa yang kau pikirkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bukan hal besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau membantu Nona Detektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau mau membunuh vampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tentu saja tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nona Detektif sudah tak berniat begitu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau bertemu vampir yang mengubah ayahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau bicara dengan vampir itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mungkin agar sepuluh tahun Nona Detektif tak terbuang sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau membuktikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami pulang duluan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Mau pulang? Ayo, minumlah lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hubungan kalian menginjak ke bagian kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bagian kedua?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak ada lagi yang menghalangi kalian. Jadi, inilah awalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ayo kalian berdua berciuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Cup cup muah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mau lihat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Boleh menggoda kami, tapi jangan keterlaluan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ko, ayo kita pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kami pamit. Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Ya. - Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Selamat malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Nazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Maaf, kami terbawa suasana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Dia jengkel karena aku menggodanya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Padahal sebelumnya, dia mau saja berciuman di depan kita meski sedang marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kurasa dia sudah berubah sejak bersama Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya. Hal seperti itu sudah bukan untuk konsumsi umum lagi baginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sangat menyentuh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo kita bersulang untuk kedewasaan Nazuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Bersulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Wah! Ada yang terbang melintas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa? Ada yang terbang, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak melihat apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak apa-apa kita pulang duluan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tidak apa-apa, kau juga bosan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku tak bosan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku bukan tipe orang yang suka berpesta dengan banyak orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sesekali tak apa-apa, tapi setiap hari rasanya melelahkan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi sebaliknya, jika malam-malam ini selalu sepi dan tenang pun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}aku akan bosan dan menjadi gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Selain itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Satu hal yang pasti, aku senang kau dan Kak Mejiro masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Jadi, itu inti dari semuanya ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, itulah intinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Aku senang bisa bersamamu, Nazuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}- Apa... - Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Apa katamu, Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Tapi ini pertama kalinya kulihat wajahmu merah merona dari depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kau bodoh, Ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Kita tak langsung pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Sebentar lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya, Nona Detektif pasti masih tidur juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Lihat, Nazuna. Di setiap lampu itu ada orangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Di sini juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}Ini bukan hal yang boleh dilakukan di depan umum, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(0,40)}{\an8}Aduh.
